Naked Souls;;1996;;R;;Sci-Fi,Thriller;;3.3;;Lyndon Chubbuck;;Brian Krause,Pamela Anderson,David Warner,Dean Stockwell,Clayton Rohner,Justina Vail,Victor Talmadge,Elizabeth Low,Deryl Carroll,Pat Millicano,Alex Manette,Yonda Davis,Jennifer Collins,Michael Papajohn,Thomas Milan,Christopher Holder,Chantel Rae,Jackie Brune;;Edward is busy trying to unlock the secrets of reading and recording people's thoughts. He is very involved with his work leaving little room for girlfriend Britt. Longstreet comes along and offers Edward a place to do his research and have unlimited funding. There are, however, ulterior motives as Edward is also somehow unlocking the secrets of eternal life.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0113926/